            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Viji front office very rude behavior actually a front office is the mirror for many organizations what ever the sector education or any.. her attitude and body language to the parents is really annoying specifically where we cannot get appointment to meet the principal of this institution,suppose to be all schools where principals are friendly natured here it us like meeting a CM.. even we can meet him if we plead.. but here that too NO. It is here all front office control. Very disappointing",
          "publisher": {
